Motormaster could finally see the islands. It had been a long trip, and
he lost track of the other Decepticons a while ago. He smiled, looking
forward to some action. He shifted his weight, so he was now plummeting
down feet first. He put his fist into the air to slow his descent, and
clenched his jaw. He hit hard, creating a thunderous noise, and a small
tremmor, as some animals were sent scurrying from the robot like
missile. He looked around, and pulled out his sword. In a large ark, he
swung, and slashed a tree ahead of him, and it easily crumpled under his
swords power. He looked back up to the sky, awaiting the others.
